434
00:42:39,480 --> 00:42:43,519
He's down the hall. Would you give
him a moment of your time?

435
00:42:43,600 --> 00:42:45,431
Sure.

436
00:42:45,800 --> 00:42:50,237
Son... Come here, son.

437
00:42:52,240 --> 00:42:56,791
- What's up, Dick?
- Who is this?

438
00:42:57,080 --> 00:43:02,313
I understood you were old pals.
This is Clarabelle's grandson.

439
00:43:02,400 --> 00:43:05,551
Sebastian!

440
00:43:05,640 --> 00:43:12,273
- I think we ought to sit down.
- Go ahead. Take a seat.

441
00:43:12,360 --> 00:43:15,875
You see, young Sebastian here...

442
00:43:16,160 --> 00:43:19,357
Can you not touch that?

443
00:43:19,440 --> 00:43:22,557
Son! All right...

444
00:43:22,640 --> 00:43:27,077
Get over there. The other chair.

445
00:43:32,160 --> 00:43:37,996
Young Sebastian here has got
himself into some nasty trouble.

446
00:43:39,680 --> 00:43:43,514
You understand what I'm saying
don't you? Go on!

447
00:43:43,600 --> 00:43:49,869
I blew a guy away.
It wasn't necessarily... my fault.

448
00:43:49,960 --> 00:43:53,873
I understand. We understand.
Nuff said.

449
00:43:53,960 --> 00:43:59,512
He did, and he's in a
probation program now.

450
00:43:59,600 --> 00:44:05,436
He needs somebody his own age
who an be a positive influence.

451
00:44:05,520 --> 00:44:10,594
So I figured he needed a kind of
probation officer, you know?

452
00:44:10,680 --> 00:44:17,233
So that he stays away from weapons.
And he wants that person to be you.

453
00:44:17,320 --> 00:44:20,835
- Yeah.
